title: Undekhi
overview: Show depicts the two aspects of the society - the power-drunk influential people who think they can get away with anything and the oppressed, subjected to years of torture, who finally decide to bring themselves to justice

tv.episodeOverview: As the dust settles after the killing, Rinku and Papaji plan to get rid of Teji. DSP Ghosh is visited by Koyal and he now has all the pieces of the Sundarban puzzle. Rinku and Ghosh try to outwit each other with the cops being on Rinku’s side and an unlikely ally on Ghosh’s.
